<PB REF="011837_0015_0F9D86FB70AEA580">
<HEAD>Hi&s;torical Proofs and Illu&s;trations being a confirmation and continuation of the View of the Progre&s;s of Socie|ty in Europe from the &s;ubver&s;ion of the Roman Em|pire to the beginning of the &s;ixteenth century.</HEAD>
